text: Alejandra Acosta (born 1 July 1986) is a Mexican volleyball player. She played at the 2006 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. 2006 Women's Pan- American Volleyball Cup, 2007 Pan American Games, 2007 Women's Pan-American Volleyball Cup, and 2008 NORCECA Beach Volleyball Circuit. She played for Jalisco. == References == == Other websites == * ALEJANDRA ACOSTA fivb.com * http://www.fivb.org/EN/BeachVolleyball/Player_DataDB.asp?No=104108 Category:1986 births Category:Mexican volleyball players Category:Living people Category:People from Jalisco
